name: In_App_Checklist_Settings__c
label: In App Checklist Settings
description: This custom settings contains all attributes used in In App Checklist

name: Legal_Entity__c
label: Legal Entity
description: Official legal name of the business entity as registered with government authorities

name: MEDDIC_Assessment__c
label: MEDDIC Assessment
description: The MEDDIC Assessment object provides structured tracking and evaluation of sales opportunities using the MEDDIC (Metrics, Economic Buyer, Decision Criteria, Decision Process, Identify Pain, Champion) qualification framework. This object enables sales teams to systematically assess and document the completeness of their opportunity qualification, ensuring consistent sales methodology application across the organization.

name: Lead_Handoff__c
label: Lead Handoff
description: The Lead Handoff object manages the formal transition process of qualified leads from Sales Development Representatives (SDRs) to Account Executives (AEs) within the L2.6 stage of the lead-to-opportunity workflow. This object ensures systematic handoff procedures, quality control, and accountability between sales development and account management teams.
